@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 3-1. 시나리오 준비: CREATOR 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "enrollment-creator-{{$uuid}}@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Enrollment Creator",
  "role": "CREATOR"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("enrollmentScenarioCreatorToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### 3-2. 시나리오 준비: STUDENT 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "enrollment-student-{{$uuid}}@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Enrollment Student",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("enrollmentScenarioStudentToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### 3-3. 시나리오 준비: Course 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{enrollmentScenarioCreatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "수강 신청 결제 취소 시나리오 {{$timestamp}}",
  "description": "신청, 결제 확정, 취소 흐름을 확인합니다.",
  "price": 10000.00,
  "capacity": 5,
  "enrollmentStartAt": "2030-06-01T10:00:00",
  "enrollmentEndAt": "2030-06-10T18:00:00",
  "courseStartAt": "2030-06-15T10:00:00",
  "courseEndAt": "2030-07-15T18:00:00"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("enrollmentScenarioCourseId", response.body.data.id);
%}

### 3-4. 시나리오 준비: Course 수동 OPEN
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{enrollmentScenarioCourseId}}/open
Authorization: Bearer {{enrollmentScenarioCreatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enrollmentEndAt": "2030-06-10T18:00:00"
}

### 3-5. STUDENT 수강 신청: PENDING 생성 및 좌석 점유
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{enrollmentScenarioCourseId}}/enrollments
Authorization: Bearer {{enrollmentScenarioStudentToken}}

> {%
    client.global.set("enrollmentScenarioEnrollmentId", response.body.data.id);
%}

### 3-6. 결제 확정: PENDING -> CONFIRMED
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/enrollments/{{enrollmentScenarioEnrollmentId}}/confirm-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{enrollmentScenarioStudentToken}}

### 3-7. 내 수강 신청 목록 조회: CONFIRMED 상태 확인
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/enrollments?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{enrollmentScenarioStudentToken}}

### 3-8. 수강 취소: CONFIRMED -> CANCELLED, 좌석 반납
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/enrollments/{{enrollmentScenarioEnrollmentId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{enrollmentScenarioStudentToken}}

### 3-9. 취소 후 Course 상세 조회: occupiedCount 감소 확인
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{enrollmentScenarioCourseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{enrollmentScenarioCreatorToken}}
